[Werbung / Ad] I've never experienced unboxing of this kind before and so I've decided to share it with you too. I hope you find it interesting as well! @oneplus_de 8T has a gorgeous 120 Hz screen, good cameras. It runs smoothly, the battery lasts a full day, and there's 5G support. You'll get two years of version upgrades and three years of security updates. 

#OnePlus8T #unboxing #smartphone #android #tech #technology #beautyoftechnology

node.text:
OnePlus have asked me if I want to check out their OnePlus Nord in the beautiful Grey Ash color and I've immediately said yes since I am very excited about all the things tech and I have actually never used an Android device. Please join me for this quick unboxing video to check what they've put inside the box apart from the smartphone itself! I am pretty impressed with the package you are getting for your money - OnePlus Nord has a great price/performance ratio.

#oneplusnord #oneplus #greyash #oneplusnordgreyash #android #androidsmartphone #tech #technology #beautyoftechnology

node.text:
Simple setup in the entry hall of our apartment. I‘ve used a walnut Catch-All from @grovemade, which is now home for my wallet and other everyday items. A trio of hidden brass hooks are perfect for keys. Speaking of hooks, I have three Hooks from @theartifox below the Catch-All. These are perfect to hand a sling or a cap on. I really like their unique design combination of aluminum and acrylic. I think both products look and work nicely together. What do you guys think?

#design #interiordesign #tech #clean #minimal #entryhall #artifox #grovemade #beautyoftechnology

node.text:
[Gifted | ad] The LE02 Wireless Speaker by Braun Audio has been designed according to the well-known 10 Design Principles by Dieter Rams. Personally, I really love the following three of them: 3) Good design is aesthetic. 7) Good design is long-lasting. 10) Good design is as little design as possible. And I think that the speaker reflects especially these three design principles the most, that’s why I like it so much. The LE02 Speaker is simply timeless and I am sure it will make me happy years ahead, not only by listening to it, but also by just looking at it.

Swipe right to see how it blends into my interior and also for some details 👌🏻

#SimplyTimeless #braun #braunaudio #LE02 #braunaudiospeaker #design #interiordesign 
#beautyoftechnology #clean #minimal #designpriciples

The AirPods Max 🎧 - I’ve got them again. The reason why I haven’t kept them first time was the price. I just could not keep a pair of headphones which costs 600€, since I already had Sony 1000 XM3 and Beoplay H9. Currently, AirPods Max are available just under 400€ here in Germany and I could get a pair for 350€, so why not 🤷🏼‍♂️

node.text:
💡Cable Management for your Inspiration! Swipe right to see how my cable management looks like! Don’t forget to save this post, to be able to check it later on when you might do your own cable management. Happy cable managing!

The stuff I used to make it:
1. Command Picture Mounting Strips to mount the power strip to the desk
2. Command Picture Mounting Strips to mount cables to the bottom of the desk
3. Velcro roll to hold cables together and attach them to the Command Picture Mounting Strips on the bottom of the desk

You can find all links to the products in my blog post, link is in the bio.

Here you go! If you have any questions, ask in the comments section below.
